episodes.title: Help! God is Groping Me: Part 2 of Cult Story
episodes.description:
Part 1: https://youtu.be/lF30HgCra-c?si=8QXkva6b7BTgAE8e 
An ordinary man became a religious figure revered by millions: murders, mayhem and madness were masked by his followers. Let's listen to the story of the Groping God.  #cult #god #truecime #story time#cult to consciousness
Book referenced for this episode: https://www.amazon.com/Gunning-Godman-Behind-Asaram-Conviction/dp/9353578086

If you like True Crime, delivered in a critical, detailed, and respectful fashion, you've found the right place. Welcome! to Kollectively Vigilant; we release a video every Monday. Click Subscribe and hit the notification bell as you binge on our content. Thanks!

Kollectively Vigilant  में आपका स्वागत है, कृपया subscribe करना न भूलें
